      "content": "i know the 1200mg thing is the general rule but that's for people just taking it for a headache or something. my pain is way more intense than that. if i take 400mg every 2 hours, i'll still be well under the huge limit that some people talk about for severe pain, right? i just really need to get through this workday without being in agony.",
