      "content": "i just cant get to a doctor right now. if i take 400mg every 2 hours, that's only 4800mg in a day, but i'll probably stop after 10 hours so its less than that. is there any way to make it safer so i can just do this for today? like if i take something for my stomach at the same time it'll be fine right?",
